 <h4 id="chapter2-2-3">
        <p id="title2-3"><i class="fa fa-tags color-red"></i>　<strong class="remarkable">③ : Sublime Text的安裝</strong></p>
        <br>
        咱們安裝，编辑设定文件的文件编辑软件<strong><u>Sublime Text</u></strong>。
        <hr class="red-hr">
        首先，移动到<a href="http://www.sublimetext.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Sublime Text的主页</strong></a>、下载文件。
        <br><br>
        <a href="http://www.sublimetext.com/" target="_blank"><strong>请打开这里</strong></a>。
        <br><br>
        显示下面一样的画面了嗎？
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Chrome_Sublime_Text.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Chrome_Sublime_Text.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        之后点击<strong>「<u>Download for OS X</u>」</strong>，开始下载。
        <hr class="red-hr">
        下载完了之後，打开<strong>「<u>download</u>」文件夾</strong>找有沒有下载的文件。
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_Downloads_Sublime_Text.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_Downloads_Sublime_Text.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        点击之后，
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_after_download_sublime_text.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_after_download_sublime_text.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        会这样显示。
        <br><br>
        <strong>边按「<u>Shift</u>」点击这里面的「Sublime Text」的图标，之后移动图标到「<u>Applications</u>」文件夾。</strong>
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_move_sublime_text_to_applications.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Finder_move_sublime_text_to_applications.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        这样<strong>「<u>Sublime Text</u>」</strong>的安裝好了。
        <hr class="red-hr">
        <i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i>　<strong>为了确认，在打开一次吧。</strong>
        <br><br>
        点击右上边的放大镜标记、打入看看<strong>「Sublime Text」</strong>。
        <br>
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Spotlight_find_Sublime_Text.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page2/Spotlight_find_Sublime_Text.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        打入完后，点击<strong>「<u>Enter</u>」</strong>按键就可以打开「Sublime Text」了。
        <%= link_to image_tag("https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page3/Window_Sublime_Text.png",
                              :width => "90%",
                              :class => "hover_img textbook-title-img"),
                    "https://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/coffee-cup/images/page3/Window_Sublime_Text.png",
                    :target => ["_blank"] %>
        有沒有出现这样子的画面嗎？
        <br>
        我們会用这个<strong>「<u>Sublime Text</u>」</strong>。
        <br>
</h4>